name: PrijsVanEenHuis.nl
tag_list: prijs, huis, makelaar, taxateur, nederland, notaris, huizen, prijzen
overview:
PrijsVanEenHuis.nl is an internet service portal about Dutch real estate.

They focus primarily on:

  • Exposing information about house sales; we offer up to date reports that contain house selling prices for a specific Dutch postal code, combined with charts and graphs that give insight for potential buyers and sellers.
  • We offer a free subscription for users to be informed automatically when real estate is sold in their nearby neigbourhood (a unique service in The Netherlands).
  • We create free real estate publications and twitter about news and facts in this area.
  • We offer advertisement possibilities for service providers operating in and around houses, targetted on specific locations /areas/ in Holland.
